---
title: Double Shrimp Fusilli with Sweet Peppers
description: It’s hard not to love fusilli! We're keeping things easy-going with a simple tomato sauce, but bringing serious flavours with Italian spices, sweet peppers and juicy shrimp. This pasta is sure to become a family favourite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fusillis-aux-crevettes-doubles-aacaae0f.jpg
